data.description: Loan is assumable, 4.5% rate --- Attention investors looking for a great rental property opportunity or owner occupants looking for a new home, this home is ready and waiting for it's new owner! This home boasts 3 beds and 2 full bathrooms with great living space, along with a spacious kitchen. Major systems; furnace, AC, water heater, electrical, plumbing have been updated in 2005 or later, which leaves the fun cosmetic upgrades. Great rents in the area for a 3 bed 2 bath if kept as a rental, and there are some great comps in the area if you chose to take it to the next level! Large lot & fenced.
